        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 32:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". As to the sickness of Hezekiah, and the miraculous sign by which the prophet Isaiah assured him of recovery, see the account in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Kings 20:1-11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
